| `site:` | Limit to domain/subdomains | `site:target.com` | Target-specific recon |
| `filetype:` / `ext:` | File type/extension | `filetype:yaml` or `ext:tfstate` | IaC configs, cloud deployments |
| `inurl:` | Keyword in URL | `inurl:swagger-ui` | Finding undocumented APIs |
| `allinurl:` | All keywords in URL | `allinurl:jira login` | Strict endpoint filtering |
| `intitle:` | Keyword in page title | `intitle:"index of /.git"` | Exposed version control |
| `intext:` | Keyword in page body | `intext:"AKIA"` | AWS key hunting |
